Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, openrc, spice-webdavd, avahi-daemon
Conflicts: systemd, systemd-sysv
Description: Package to add Spice and Avahi daemon configuration for OpenRC.
 This package will add the boot scripts to use spice-webdavd and avahi-daemon
 with OpenRC in Nitrux.

